('1236', '78', 'body_0_text', 'Sitindustrie Valvometal started manufacturing valves for the energy industry in 1955 in its plant in Valduggia, Italy, and today is regarded as a very important supplier of ball, gate, globe and check valves.'),
('1237', '78', '_body_0_text', 'field_59ecd96f5b47e'),
('1238', '78', 'body_1_text', 'The complete range of valves can be produced in forged and cast carbon steel, stainless steel and special alloy. Our company is mainly focused to critical applications in oil &amp; gas, petrochemical, power generation, nuclear, food and dairy industries.'),
('1239', '78', '_body_1_text', 'field_59ecd96f5b47e'),
