('1242', '78', 'body_3_text', 'The continuous investments in R&amp;D together with the willing to satisfying our clients’ needs , allowed Sitindustrie Valvometal to implement new technologies and innovative solutions for the most severe applications.\r\nFurthermore, Sitindustrie Valvometal, thanks to its more than 60 years’ experience in the sector and the commitment of the people who are part of it, is a reliable supplier for the most demanding customers.'),
